  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package contains a richly described primary claim whose provenance appears well-established through ValidationResult nodes; however the Claim node itself carries no prov:wasDerivedFrom link to any Evidence, rendering it an orphan claim under W-EP-01.",
